View → reusable virtual table
Stored Procedure → stored SQL program (can take input/output)
CTE → temporary readable query block
Subquery → query inside another query
Window Function → calculate over a row window (ranking, totals


| Feature                             | VIEW                  | STORED PROCEDURE      | CTE                   | SUBQUERY               | WINDOW FUNCTION              |
| ----------------------------------- | --------------------- | --------------------- | --------------------- | ---------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| Definition                          | Virtual table         | Precompiled SQL block | Temporary named query | Query inside query     | Function over window of rows |
| Stored in DB                        | ✅ Yes                 | ✅ Yes                 | ❌ No                  | ❌ No                   | ❌ No                         |
| Lifetime                            | Permanent             | Permanent             | Only during query     | Only during query      | Only during query            |
| Parameters                          | ❌                     | ✅                     | ❌                     | ❌                      | ❌                            |
| Use Case                            | Reusable SELECT logic | Automation, data ops  | Simplify query        | Conditional data fetch | Ranking, totals              |
| Supports DML (INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE) | Limited               | ✅                     | ❌                     | ❌                      | ❌                            |
